-- Spot Gold Declines for a Second Day, Dropping 0.2% to $1,615.20 an Ounce
-- B y   P h o e b e   S e d g m a n
-- 2012-01-08T23:12:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-08/spot-gold-declines-for-a-second-day-dropping-0-2-to-1-615-20-an-ounce.html
Gold for immediate delivery declined
0.2 percent to $1,615.20 an ounce, while bullion for February
delivery in  New York  traded little changed at $1,616.40 an
ounce. Silver for March delivery advanced 0.2 percent to $28.745
an ounce.  To contact the reporter on this story:
